data.description: Welcome to this meticulously maintained 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom ranch home in charming Dacula. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by beautiful hardwood floors that seamlessly flow through the common areas, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. The heart of this home is the open concept living/dining/kitchen area, where you'll find a cozy brick fireplace in the living room and a delightful seating area in the bay window. The kitchen boasts stained wood cabinets, stainless steel appliances, and a convenient breakfast bar, making it a perfect space for both everyday living and entertaining. A unique feature of this home is the large separate sunroom/bonus room. With vaulted ceilings and a door leading to the backyard, this space provides flexibility for various uses – whether it be a relaxing sunroom or an additional entertainment area. Convenience is key, with the laundry closet located in the hall behind a beautiful sliding barn door. The generously sized primary suite is a retreat with ample natural light, a walk-in closet, and an ensuite bathroom featuring double vanities and a separate shower and tub. Two additional well-proportioned bedrooms share a full bathroom in the hallway. Step outside to the backyard, where you'll discover plenty of greenspace to enjoy outdoor activities. The attached 2-car garage adds to the convenience of this home. Located near Dacula High School, this property offers easy access to shopping and dining options, as well as the nearby highway 316. Notable upgrades include a newer AC and water heater, providing peace of mind for years to come. Don't miss the opportunity to make this well-loved and upgraded ranch home your own – schedule a showing today!
